资源)\n- [ ] T050: 创建 e2e_integration_test.go - 测试 Informer 事件处理 (Add/Update/Delete)\n\n---\n\n## Verification\n\n- [ ] V001: 运行所有 Clientset 测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Clientset\"`\n- [ ] V002: 运行所有 AgentRuntime CRUD 测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"AgentRuntime\"`\n- [ ] V003: 运行所有 CodeInterpreter 测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"CodeInterpreter\"`\n- [ ] V004: 运行所有 Informer Factory 测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Informer\"`\n- [ ] V005: 运行所有 Lister 测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Lister\"`\n- [ ] V006: 运行所有 Fake Client 测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Fake\"`\n- [ ] V007: 运行所有 E2E 流程测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"E2E\"`\n- [ ] V008: 运行完整测试套件 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/...`\n- [ ] V009: 验证测试覆盖率报告 - `go test -cover ./test/e2e/...`\n- [ ] V010: 运行集成场景测试 - `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Integration\"`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n确保以下依赖已安装:\n- `go >= 1.21`\n- `k8s.io/client-go`\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/envtest` (用于集成测试)\n\n---\n\n## Test Execution Notes\n\n1. **Unit Tests**: 使用 fake clientset 进行快速测试\n2. **Integration Tests**: 使用 envtest 启动本地 API server\n3. **E2E Tests**: 需要真实 Kubernetes 集群 (使用 `make e2e-test` 或跳过)\n4. 使用 `-short` flag 跳过需要集群的测试: `go test -short ./test/e2e/...`\n\n---\n\n## Reference\n\n- Delta Spec: `delta-spec.md` (AR-041 section)\n- Client-go library: `pkg/client/`\n- API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md"},"error":"You must read file /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md before overwriting it. Use the Read tool first","time":{"start":1775884967393,"end":1775884967400}}}}
